divs: Sighting DetailsIt was a bright, sunny day. Lots of birds singing. No other noises. I was taking photos of a historical mansion and I found an object in the sky of one photo once I got home. I never saw this while I was there, nor did i hear it. I take careful notes of the ambient sounds out there as I usually record for EVPS (often I am successful). there were no planes, helis or anything else there,that I heard. It doesn't look like a bird to me. it appears to be too large and pretty high up in relation to the tree and the house. I would like professional input please
